---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AvengersPoster from '@/assets/images/endgame_poster.webp';
import PlayEdSheeran from '@/assets/images/play-ed-sheeran.jpg';
import classes from '@/data/styles.json';

const title = 'Profile';
const description =
  'I help forward-thinking companies build performant, accessible, and beautiful web applications using the modern React ecosystem.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="mx-auto mb-32 max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 border-t border-zinc-200 pt-12 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-24 dark:border-zinc-800"
    >
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 lg:col-span-5">
        <div class="relative aspect-[4/5] w-full overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
          <img
            alt="John working"
            class="h-full w-full object-cover grayscale transition-all duration-700 hover:grayscale-0"
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBTnXV80pcXHMYaH150XP-3gZgytwJ6akJ3hJXVLW8fkhf9-5bAo-u9UDwZZdCNk3jwaeklcNUM61SMm0bGO6Eeocx8XeVaGv0bjLB28s9AE7WZQlFY9qjrpa7RwEM1huX60kSBmb1wF_mQSLehoWuiG8tSM-0H2UitFZ3UiN6OteySjxY56x9J7Foi9VgnJC6sYV9hW69jwSFESSx-jOjqOkVx5LyPBTL8Yu0QSSAwu2VYO4RrSxqiZ0yElDb_jAeVOqhLe9Mi1lk"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="order-1 flex flex-col justify-center lg:order-2 lg:col-span-7">
        <h2 class={classes.preHeading}>The Philosophy</h2>
        <h3 class={classes.heading}>
          Customer Obsessed. <br class="hidden md:block" />Solution Driven.
        </h3>
        <div
          class="prose dark:prose-invert text-md max-w-none leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400"
        >
          <p class="mb-6">
            Great software isn't just about clean code; it's about solving real problems for real
            people. My philosophy centers on empathyâ€”understanding the user's journey and crafting
            interfaces that feel intuitive and effortless.
          </p>
          <p>
            Every pixel serves a purpose, and every interaction is an opportunity to delight. I
            believe that technical excellence is the baseline, but the true value lies in how
            effectively that technology serves the human on the other side of the screen.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section
    class="mb-32 border-y border-zinc-100 bg-zinc-50 py-24 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900/50"
  >
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class={classes.preHeading}>The Approach</h2>
        <h3 class={classes.heading}>Precision Meets Purpose.</h3>
        <p class={classes.secondaryText}>Secondard</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div
          class="group rounded-2xl border border-zinc-100 bg-white p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-800"
        >
          <div
            class="mb-6 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-zinc-100 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110 dark:bg-zinc-700"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">architecture</span
            >
          </div>
          <h4 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Structure</h4>
          <p class="leading-relaxed text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400">
            Building scalable architectures that grow with the product. I focus on modular,
            maintainable codebases that allow teams to move fast without breaking things.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="group rounded-2xl border border-zinc-100 bg-white p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-800"
        >
          <div
            class="mb-6 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-zinc-100 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110 dark:bg-zinc-700"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">speed</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Performance</h4>
          <p class="leading-relaxed text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400">
            Optimizing for speed because every millisecond counts. From efficient rendering to
            bundle analysis, I ensure the experience is snappy for every user.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="group rounded-2xl border border-zinc-100 bg-white p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-800"
        >
          <div
            class="mb-6 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-zinc-100 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110 dark:bg-zinc-700"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">devices</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Adaptability</h4>
          <p class="leading-relaxed text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400">
            Creating fluid designs that work seamlessly on any device. Accessibility and
            responsiveness aren't afterthoughts; they are core to my development process.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto mb-32 max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="flex flex-col">
      <h2 class="mb-6 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-400">
        Beyond the Keyboard
      </h2>
      <h3 class="mb-6 text-4xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Life Offline.</h3>
      <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400">
        My work is fueled by the experiences I gather when I step away from the desk.
      </p>
      <div class="hidden h-1 w-20 rounded-full bg-zinc-200 lg:block dark:bg-zinc-800"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-24">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:col-span-12">
        <div
          class="group/card flex flex-col justify-between rounded-2xl border border-zinc-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900"
        >
          <div class="flex h-full flex-col justify-between">
            <div>
              <div class="mb-4 flex items-center justify-between">
                <span
                  class="inline-block rounded-xl bg-blue-50 p-3 text-blue-600 dark:bg-blue-900/20 dark:text-blue-400"
                >
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined">flight_takeoff</span>
                </span>
                <span
                  class="rounded-full bg-zinc-100 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-500 dark:bg-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-400"
                >
                  Next: Japan
                </span>
              </div>
              <h4 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Traveler</h4>
              <p class="mb-6 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400">
                Exploring new cultures and finding inspiration in the unplanned. Travel teaches me
                adaptability and helps me see problems from new perspectives.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 border-t border-zinc-100 pt-6 dark:border-zinc-800">
              <div
                class="cursor-default rounded-xl bg-zinc-50 p-3 text-center transition-colors hover:bg-blue-50 dark:bg-zinc-800/50 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/10"
              >
                <div
                  class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 transition-colors group-hover/card:text-blue-600 dark:text-white dark:group-hover/card:text-blue-400"
                >
                  4
                </div>
                <div class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-400">
                  Continents
                </div>
              </div>
              <div
                class="cursor-default rounded-xl bg-zinc-50 p-3 text-center transition-colors hover:bg-blue-50 dark:bg-zinc-800/50 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/10"
              >
                <div
                  class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 transition-colors group-hover/card:text-blue-600 dark:text-white dark:group-hover/card:text-blue-400"
                >
                  18
                </div>
                <div class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-400">
                  Countries
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="flex flex-col justify-between rounded-2xl border border-zinc-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-shadow duration-300 hover:shadow-md dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900"
        >
          <div class="flex h-full flex-col justify-between">
            <div>
              <span
                class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-xl bg-purple-50 p-3 text-purple-600 dark:bg-purple-900/20 dark:text-purple-400"
              >
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">psychology</span>
              </span>
              <h4 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">The 'Why'</h4>
              <p class="mb-6 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400">
                I code because I love the logic, but I create because I love the impact.
                Disconnecting allows me to reconnect with my core creativity.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-t border-zinc-100 pt-6 dark:border-zinc-800">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">battery_charging_full</span>
                <span>Recharging Creativity</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-100 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm md:col-span-2 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900"
        >
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span
              class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-xl bg-red-50 p-3 text-red-600 dark:bg-red-900/20 dark:text-red-400"
            >
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">movie_filter</span>
            </span>
            <h4 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">Media Enthusiast</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400">
              Curating a mental library of films, music, and books. Great storytelling in media
              influences how I tell stories through interfaces.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 border-t border-zinc-100 pt-6 sm:grid-cols-3 dark:border-zinc-800"
          >
            <div class="group flex items-center gap-3">
              <Image
                src={PlayEdSheeran}
                alt="Play Ed Sheeran Album Cover"
                format="avif"
                quality={85}
                loading="lazy"
                densities={[1, 2]}
                class="h-28 w-28 rounded-sm object-cover shadow-sm transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105"
              />
              <div class="min-w-0">
                <div
                  class="mb-0.5 flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-400"
                >
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xs">headphones</span> On Repeat
                </div>
                <div class="truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">
                  After Hours
                </div>
                <div class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-500">The Weeknd</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="group flex items-center gap-3">
              <Image
                src={AvengersPoster}
                alt="Portrait of Shavar"
                format="avif"
                quality={85}
                loading="lazy"
                densities={[1, 2]}
                class="h-28 w-28 rounded-sm object-cover shadow-sm transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105"
              />

              <div class="min-w-0">
                <div
                  class="mb-0.5 flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-400"
                >
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xs">movie</span> Favorite
                </div>
                <div class="truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">
                  Avengers: Endgame
                </div>
                <div class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-500">Russo Brothers</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="group flex items-center gap-3">
              <img
                alt="Book"
                class="h-14 w-14 rounded-lg object-cover shadow-sm transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105"
                src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBNP1a4MzokfapYCPrJhi33Y_o8eDqIqKGs_jDq3XXrRgPIMaAKeQ45-DO8R2c-1m1euodZ7KP5aBvEohYbv2M1_9xO9gv30nkfHkslbbT0pr7kiD06MvN9ggh6qvjTg29Lx2BbAl6lnUsoT8aaY6nIcVh1R0G1a9Im1YwgvnVC1mBKHC113FAXPg1VogOxCzRdDIilhAGMXLS2UG6Yu9mRxupqPHQKhsEMH-zRBOfleDDqfGSrGdMD5oAt6sCoTSnpYv8eK3f9PfI"
              />
              <div class="min-w-0">
                <div
                  class="mb-0.5 flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-400"
                >
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xs">menu_book</span> Reading
                </div>
                <div class="truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">
                  Deep Work
                </div>
                <div class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-500">Cal Newport</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
